"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-21-After-8-years-a-more-mature-Ye-Shiwen-heads-back-to-Summer-Olympics-1uBKthUENtm-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Ye Shiwen of China wins the women's 200-meter individual breaststroke gold medal at the 19th Asian Games in Hangzhou, east CHina's Zhejiang Province, September 28, 2023.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9439172089219011, \"rank\": 0.05924148565324569, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5953223610725837e-16, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Ye Shiwen, 28, will participate in the upcoming 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris for the Chinese national swimming team after securing qualification in late April.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ye Shiwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\"}, {\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999967159259806, \"rank\": 3.284084882699639e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9913959050015978, \"rank\": 0.007658994463435791, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been eight years since her last appearance at the Games.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I gave a 100 percent effort there,\\\" Ye told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}, {\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 701, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"score\": 0.9488581283319821, \"rank\": 0.04986834605020466, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't in my best form, either physically or mentally, before the final.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a long time to adjust my mindset.\\\"\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ye became an Olympic gold medalist in 2012, when she won the women's 200-meter individual medley and 400-meter individual medley titles at the London Games when she was just 16 years old.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later, however, Ye suffered one of the biggest setbacks in her career.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished in fourth place in the 200-meter individual medley final and failed to reach the 400-meter individual medley final at the Rio de Janeiro Games.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Feeling frustrated, Ye stayed away from the swimming pool and pursued other activities in an effort to ease her pain.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She became a full-time student at Tsinghua University Law School in 2017 and graduated this year.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tsinghua_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tsinghua University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tsinghua_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tsinghua_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says she grew more mature during this period, and returned to the pool with a better mindset in 2019.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ye Shiwen competes in the women's 200-meter individual breaststroke final at the Chinese domestic Olympic trials in Shenzhen, south China's Guangdong Province, April 24, 2024.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ye Shiwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\"}, {\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9913959050015978, \"rank\": 0.007658994463435791, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"score\": 0.999999991882305, \"rank\": 7.416756054083817e-09, \"text\": \"Shenzhen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\"}, {\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9439172089219011, \"rank\": 0.05924148565324569, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guangdong Province\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  \\\"The first time I finally got my mindset right was at the World Aquatics Championships in Gwangju in 2019,\\\" Ye said.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5992836540083928e-18, \"text\": \"Gwangju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From 2013 to 2019, it took me six years to do so.\\\"\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ye finished the women's 200-meter individual breaststroke event in 2:22.55 at China's Olympic trials in Shenzhen, Guangdong Province, in April.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}, {\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9439172089219011, \"rank\": 0.05924148565324569, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"score\": 0.999999991882305, \"rank\": 7.416756054083817e-09, \"text\": \"Shenzhen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guangdong Province\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even though she qualified for the 2024 Olympics in that event, she failed to advance beyond the preliminary competition in her favored 400-meter individual medley.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, Ye did not let the failure bring her to her knees.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, she took three days to shake off the frustration, and then secured her spot in Paris.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999967159259806, \"rank\": 3.284084882699639e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think swimming is something I love and enjoy.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's not like I have to do it,\\\" Ye told CMG.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655714662662799e-16, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}, {\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"score\": 0.9488581283319821, \"rank\": 0.04986834605020466, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I enjoy everything about it, including the fact that I can perform better in competitions after working hard in training.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I even enjoy the pain of training, because after I beat the pain and learn that I have done better than last week, I feel so accomplished.\\\"\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": []}]}"